Lithonia Lighting offers the FEN Narrow Industrial Enclosure as an attractive shallow lighting enclosure for use as industrial lighting fixtures. The FEN features impact-resistant acrylic lenses and thermally protected, energy saving ballasts which minimize energy consumption while maximizing lifespan as well. These features allow the FEN to perform in various settings such as parking garages, food processing plants and other areas where the use of industrial lighting systems is required. 
 Quality performance and maximal profits are the key difference in Acuity Brands’ lighting technologies. Industrial grade lighting solutions offer sustainable features to meet all standards in all applications. Acuity Brands’ ever-expanding line of lighting fixtures, which includes lighting renovation solutions to industrial fluorescent lighting technologies, provide quality, energy-efficiency and cost effectiveness.
